name: Height-102
description: This is one of my works, the source of inspiration for which is my hometown in Russia and a monument to the war of 1945. The sculpture, called "Motherland calls", is located in the city of Volgograd, during the war, the place where the sculpture is currently located was called ''Height-102"  This is an attempt to portray a futuristic picture of a city where skyscrapers dominate the cultural heritage.
